=========================
= PapaBench SCJ version =
=========================

The project provides an implementation of PapaBench for Safety-critical Java (SCJ).
The logic of the PapaBench implementation is provided by the project papabench-core.
This project encapsulates the logic into SCJ-specific constructs (periodic handlers, SCJ-specific memory allocation).

For further information, please, visit the project page:
http://d3s.mff.cuni.cz/~malohlava/projects/jpapabench/

